description: Fighting in Gaza is down sharply. Aid deliveries are rising rapidly. Israel has withdrawn most of its troops. The Israel-Hamas war has entered a new phase.
title: With little fanfare, Gaza war enters a new stage, from high to low intensity

description: If the current conflict between J. Cole, Kendrick Lamar and Drake feels confusing, it's because the artists often hailed as hip-hop's "big three" have never played by the same rules.
title: Can rap beef exist when no one agrees on what's being fought for?
